{"tid":2490814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國研究：能從空氣採集人類DNA","createTime":"2021-04-16T01:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T04:35:49.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2b1f74e41529e5436164453d2f9d5e832eead3","tid":2490814,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w820/s/s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Vt93tea0BM7GrYDNHEi6zw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/W3Dn7n1OfYb8ok1W9ZYurQ--~B/aD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/health_concept_154/b8da9a9258a1ba15d54133e3b8ed7dec\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs-yimg-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw820%2Fs%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FVt93tea0BM7GrYDNHEi6zw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTY0MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FW3Dn7n1OfYb8ok1W9ZYurQ--~B%2FaD0xMjAwO3c9MTIwMDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhealth_concept_154%2Fb8da9a9258a1ba15d54133e3b8ed7dec&h=ff3032bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E8%83%BD%E5%BE%9E%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%8E%A1%E9%9B%86dna-%E6%96%B0%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E8%AE%93%E4%BA%BA%E9%A1%9E%E7%84%A1%E6%89%80%E9%81%81%E5%BD%A2-090000037.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%25A0%2594%25E7%25A9%25B6-%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%25BE%259E%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%258E%25A1%25E9%259B%2586dna-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%258A%2580%25E8%25A1%2593%25E8%25AE%2593%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25A1%259E%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2589%2580%25E9%2581%2581%25E5%25BD%25A2-090000037.html&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=e29557a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6-%E8%83%BD%E5%BE%9E%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%8E%A1%E9%9B%86dna-%E6%96%B0%E6%8A%80%E8%A1%93%E8%AE%93%E4%BA%BA%E9%A1%9E%E7%84%A1%E6%89%80%E9%81%81%E5%BD%A2-090000037.html</a><br />\n<br />\n人類的遺傳物質是DNA (Deoxyribose Nucleic Acid)，又名為脫氧核糖核酸，它的主要功能是資訊儲存，可傳遞遺傳的資訊。近日倫敦瑪麗女王大學的科學家研究發現，可從空氣中收集並檢測到動物和人類DNA，並表示這一發現可為法醫研究、人類學研究提供新技術，甚至有助於了解新冠病毒的傳播。<br />\n<br />\n研究在《PeerJ》雜誌上的文章指，科研人員從養有裸鼴鼠的房間裏採集空氣樣本，及後以新技術發現可檢測到裸鼴鼠的DNA。他們甚至從空氣樣本中檢測出了人類DNA，這意味着該技術或能用於法醫採樣。倫敦瑪麗女王大學高級講師和文章第一作者 Elizabeth Clare 指出，據首次公佈的數據表明，可從空氣中收集動物的eDNA（即環境中有機DNA）。<br />\n<br />\nElizabeth Clare 續指，該技術除了用於動物研究，也可應在更廣泛領域，包括法醫學、人類學，甚至醫學領域，該項技術都有潛在價值，例如可幫助了解新冠肺炎等空氣傳播疾病如何傳播，也幫助我們在難以到達的地方，如洞穴對動物進行調查。<br />\n<br />\n相關研究成果已發表於學術期刊《PeerJ》，題為《eDNAir: proof of concept that animal DNA can be collected from air sampling》（eDNAir：動物 DNA 可以從空氣樣本中收集的概念證明）。"},{"pid":"675e40d0cab410291a8f4edf2be2a763838c33e5","tid":2490814,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:37:05.000Z","msg":"英國研究再一次擴闊人類嘅想像力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52154a5fa8743795ecce62117242cbd51ea05b95","tid":2490814,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:38:17.000Z","msg":"Environmental DNA Can Be Pulled from the Air<br />\n<br />\nA proof-of-concept study uses eDNA in the air to detect mammals, expanding the technique beyond aquatic sampling.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.the-scientist.com/news-opinion/environmental-dna-can-be-pulled-from-the-air-68645\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.the-scientist.com%2Fnews-opinion%2Fenvironmental-dna-can-be-pulled-from-the-air-68645&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwDv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=76af2653\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.the-scientist.com/news-opinion/environmental-dna-can-be-pulled-from-the-air-68645</a>"},{"pid":"61caf809491b360ddc3da6f89334d64d96af062e","tid":2490814,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ce47107b16c5989ae84bfcca74d233899dda17","tid":2490814,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:45:24.000Z","msg":"仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8a0eb25a06f751b2fcb152661b14ab4b4b5a457","tid":2490814,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:45:29.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">我可以隔空抽插</span>"},{"pid":"128c6526a257f8666ddfb6a078305739e8f7bb7f","tid":2490814,"uid":255940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:48:36.000Z","msg":"cia鳩up用黎呃鳩d犯既高科技<br />\n原來有實現既一日"},{"pid":"23a498c21273dc7448b644f49aee19ba07d5edce","tid":2490814,"uid":393512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75cc4b4959cccecd92d0181c7e031586c135413","tid":2490814,"uid":29663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:52:53.000Z","msg":"可惜係英國研究"},{"pid":"81d1efb4190253078ec016b73e3d436fd9f09d14","tid":2490814,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:54:07.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係支那研究"},{"pid":"9063f8054c2ce692a570fe5b87b999ddbb1c9cff","tid":2490814,"uid":224196,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T01:56:26.000Z","msg":"過幾十年就會有研究證明<br />\n<br />\n只要有個男人路過一個空間<br />\n<br />\n之後有另一個女人路過果個空間<br />\n<br />\n個女人就會懷孕"},{"pid":"8b2453427f7b1bdc662e73ae54e276077988c59d","tid":2490814,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9063f8054c2ce692a570fe5b87b999ddbb1c9cff","tid":2490814,"uid":224196,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2